  "Complementary sequences activate the immune system against the mRNA": "",
  "Non-complementary sequences would destroy all mRNA in the cell": "",
  "Antisense drugs work through complementary base pairing: the synthetic oligonucleotide hybridizes with the target mRNA, forming a double-stranded structure that blocks ribosome binding or triggers RNase H degradation of the mRNA.": "",
  "Scientists studying the origin of life propose the 'RNA world' hypothesis, which suggests RNA preceded DNA as the genetic material. A researcher points to ribozymes as key evidence. What are ribozymes and why do they support this hypothesis?": "",
  "Ribozymes are proteins that help RNA fold correctly due to the well-established relationship between ribozymes trends and broader outcomes": "",
